[DhtmlXQ_comment11]After playing the palcorner cannon, red's opening has become the 56 Cannons with 3rd Pawn Advancement vs the Sandwiched Horse Defense with left elephant variation.||This opening was once very popular in the mid 80's, but has gradually declined in usage in the recent years.||In this variation, the tempo of the game is slow and most of the time, the game would become a standoff.||Red would choose to develop his pieces into his ideal formation before starting to attack, thereby  slowing the pace of the game.　[/DhtmlXQ_comment11]
